  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Constraint<T extends IPatternMatch>  
    ConstraintAdapter
    The constraint adapter class is used to collect the constraints and deal with their maintenance for a given EMF instance model.
    MarkerEraserJob
    The job is used to remove a problem marker from the Problems View of Eclipse when the constraint violation is no longer present.
    MarkerPlacerJob
    The job is used to create a problem marker in the Problems View of Eclipse upon constraint violation.
    MarkerUpdaterJob
    The job is used to update a problem marker in the Problems View of Eclipse.
    ValidationPartListener
    The PartListener is used to observe EditorPart close actions.
